Paper: hep-th/9505050

Date: 1995-05-09

Title: Action functionals for strings in four dimensions

Authors: Mikhail Alexandrov

Comments: 9 pages, LaTeX, 7 figures

Journal-ref: Lett. Math. Phys. 37 (1996) 181

All possible action functionals on the space of surfaces in ${\bf R}^4$ thatdepend only on first and second derivatives of the functions, entering theequation of the surface, and satisfy the condition of invariance with respectto rigid motions are described.